--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 Usage
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

 ./test-harness.plx -f FILENAME		run test-harness with FILENAME config file

 ./test-harness.plx -nf FILENAME	run test harness with given test-harness-
                                    config file, but don't run tests (for cross-
                                    compiling machines)

 ./test-harness.plx -tf FILENAME	run test harness with given test-harness-
                                    config file, but don't configure and build--
                                    only run tests (for cross-compiling 
                                    machines)

 ./test-harness.plx -p FILENAME		parse FILENAME config file and exit

 ./test-harness.plx -g FILENAME		generate commented config file (with 
									defaults) named FILENAME and exit

 ./test-harness.plx -sg FILENAME	generate uncommented config file (with 
									defaults) named FILENAME and exit

 ./test-harness.plx -h				print test-harness help/usage information
									and exit

 Note: if "./test-harness.plx" doesn't work on your machine, try 
       "perl test-harness.plx"

